<big>Umurenge wa Rubona ni umwe mu mirenge 14 igize akarere ka Rwamagana. Uherereye mu majyepfo y'akarere, ukaba uhana imbibi n'umurenge wa Mwurire mu majyaruguru, Munyaga na Kigabiro mu burasirazuba, Nzige mu burengerazuba n'akarere ka Ngoma mu majyepfo, aho bigabanywa n'ikiyaga cya Mugesera.
Umurenge wa Rubona ugizwe n'utugari dutandatu (6) ari two:
1. Byinza
2. Kabatasi
3. Kabuye
4. Karambi
5. Mabare
6. Nawe.
Natwo tugizwe n'imidugudu 36.
Umurenge wa Rubona ufite ubuso bwa 5,53 km<sup>2, ukaba utuwe n'abaturage bageze ku 21.640(2009)</sup></big>
